        <h3>What's New in 2026.03.20</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Streaming mode re-enabled (Beta) — real-time transcription is back, now powered by large-v3-turbo's 4-layer decoder. The medium model's 24-layer decoder caused hallucination loops in streaming (hypothesis repeated endlessly, zero segments confirmed); turbo's lightweight decoder processes audio chunks fast enough to keep up with live speech. Toggle in Preferences → "Streaming mode (Beta)".</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
          All transcription happens 100% locally on your device.
        </p>
      ]]></description>
